file_content.text: Think we could wait in a lounge or something? Or maybe, I don't know, go speeder browsing?
I still don't see why we're waiting at all. I'm telling you, it's just a simple tweak to the motivator coupling.
Hyper-actuator = broken
No, it's the coupling! The actuator's fine, Twelve. I fixed it, remember?
Fix = put in order, repair, correct // Hurley = creating new definitions of words?
Wow. That's just hurtful, you know? I mean, I don't second guess you about the ship's sensors, do I?
You do, Hurley, at every opportunity. You never let any of us forget how much more brilliant you are about everything.
Ha! Long as you can get under Geth's skin, don't ever change, Hurl.
I have more important matters to attend to.
You. Have their ship fueled and ready.
Sure.
[Walk away]
Oh, real nice. Way to help me and Officer Grouchface get into space to shoot down the enemy!
Salana! Make fun of me all you want, but you really ought to be more careful.
Please. Ever known me to be a kiss-up?
No, and that's what's got me worried....
We're seventeenth in the repair queue, by the way.
Great. Thought you had pull, Geth, what with your parents being big deals and all.
Hey--you look like someone with some pull. Think you could get our ship to the front of the fix-it list?
You know I hate when you mention them....
Got more important stuff to deal with.
I'm busy.
Wow. Here I didn't think there was anyone worse than Uppity Aven. Imagine the dynamic that would bring to the crew.
Thanks. You're way more helpful than Sergeant Stuffy here. Could trade places, help us take down some Republic scum!
